 

 

How to Play – 

 

Objective is to get a score of 300 or above. 

Knock down all ten pins in one shot for a strike, or ten in two shots for a spare. 

Use the A and D keys to position where to throw the ball from. 

Hold down Space key to charge up the ball, which is determined by the power slider. 

Let go of space key to launch the ball. 

 

A link to the public repository- 

https://github.com/mutant646/10-pin-bowling.git 

 

